<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT65">
<l>cūtāva teṉṉeñcat teṇṇiṉēṉ coṉmālai</l>
<l>mātāya mālavaṉai mātavaṉai yātāṉum</l>
<l>vallavā cintit tiruppēṟkku vaikuntat</l>
<l>tillaiyō collī riṭam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have resolved in my heart that [this] is the means:</l>
<l>tell [me], is there no place in Vaikuṇṭha for me</l>
<l>who am thinking, as much as [I] can, of the garland of names</l>
<l>of the handsome Māl, Mādhava?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
